OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSpain plans menstrual leave
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin new law for those with  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsevere pain                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Spain is planning to introduce medical 
OL,6, leave for women who suffer from severe 
OL,7, period pain, media reports suggest.    
OL,9,FA draft bill says women could have     
OL,10,Fthree days of leave a month - extended 
OL,11,Fto five in some circumstances.         
OL,13,FBut politicians warned that the draft -
OL,14,Fleaked to Spanish media outlets - was  
OL,15,Fstill being worked on.                 
OL,17,FIf passed, it would be the first such  
OL,18,Flegal entitlement in Europe. Only a    
OL,19,Fhandful of countries around the world  
OL,20,Fhave such legislation in place.        
